" data-end=\"2806\" \/>\u274c Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, <strong data-start=\"2835\" data-end=\"2855\">kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/strong> khi\u1ebfn n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t nhanh.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2885\" data-end=\"3180\">\ud83d\udccc <strong data-start=\"2888\" data-end=\"2907\">Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00fang:<\/strong><br data-start=\"2907\" data-end=\"2910\" \/>\u2705 <strong data-start=\"2912\" data-end=\"2951\">Th\u0103m kh\u00e1m &amp; ph\u00e2n t\u00edch da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<br data-start=\"2991\" data-end=\"2994\" \/>\u2705 <strong data-start=\"2996\" data-end=\"3033\">\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb theo ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a<\/strong> k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<br data-start=\"3091\" data-end=\"3094\" \/>\u2705 <strong data-start=\"3096\" data-end=\"3156\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da khoa h\u1ecdc, ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3187\" data-end=\"3245\"><strong data-start=\"3191\" data-end=\"3243\">3. Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i Dr.Anmytas<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3247\" data-end=\"3481\">\ud83d\udc49 <strong data-start=\"3250\" data-end=\"3279\">\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 MC1-R:<\/strong><br data-start=\"3279\" data-end=\"3282\" \/>\u2714\ufe0f <strong data-start=\"3285\" data-end=\"3335\">T\u0103ng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thay da, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 s\u1eabm m\u00e0u<\/strong>.<br data-start=\"3336\" data-end=\"3339\" \/>\u2714\ufe0f <strong data-start=\"3342\" data-end=\"3367\">\u1ee8c ch\u1ebf melanin t\u1eeb g\u1ed1c<\/strong>, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nguy c\u01a1 n\u00e1m quay tr\u1ed